CBRE is excited to offer, for lease, 15 South Road, Braybrook.

This is a truly unique property, offering both outstanding functional warehousing & excellent local amenity.

The inner west location boasts unbeatable proximity to the Port of Melbourne (5km*) and Melbourne's CBD (8.5km*).

This property won't last long given the long list of draw-card features including:
+ Low site coverage, with large floodlit concrete hardstand
+ 3 phase existing power supply
+ 6 container height roller doors
+ Wash bay
+ Full drive around facility
+ High clearance and clear span warehouse
+ Fitted offices & full staff amenities
+ Ability to operate 24 hours
+ Building area: 2,331sqm*
+ Site area: 14,000sqm*
+ Short stroll to Tottenham train station
+ Neighbouring retail precinct with full shopping centre

Contact the team at CBRE for more information and to arrange an inspection.

*approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer, for lease, 4 South Road, Braybrook.

This former engineering facility has been has been completely refurbished and includes a new concrete warehouse slab, new roof and fully refurbished offices and amenities. The property is strategically located in the inner west, only 8km* to the CBD and 5km* to the Port of Melbourne.

Key features to note are the following:
+ Total building area: 5,260sqm*
+ Total site area: 7,542sqm*
+ Multiple overhead cranes in full serviced and working order
+ Operational wash bay
+ Drive through truck access
+ Large rear yard accessible via the side street (Bank St)
+ Huge power supply
+ Short stroll to Tottenham train station
+ Adjoining shopping centre with wide range of retail options
+ Commercial 2 zoning to suit a range of potential uses


Contact the exclusive agency team at CBRE today to arrange an inspection.


*approx.

CBRE is excited to present 81-85 Ashley Street, Braybrook, for lease.

Recently undergoing a complete refurbishment this property is suitable for all occupier types.

Located in a convenient inner west location providing excellent access to major arterials including Princes Highway and the Western Ring Road. 

Situated approximately 5km west of the Port of Melbourne, 9km west of the CBD and 14km south of Melbourne Airport.

81-85 Ashley Street boasts the following key features:
+ Recently refurbished facility with upgraded internal and external facilities
+ Total Site Area: 20,095sqm*
+ Total Building Area: 9,319sqm*
+ High internal clearance warehouse: 8,819sqm*
+ Large office and amenities area: 500sqm*
+ ESFR sprinkler system
+ Excellent exposure to Ashley Street
+ Seven (7) on-grade roller doors
+ Rear hardstand area
+ Ample on-site car parking
+ Commercial 2 Zone

Please contact the listed CBRE agents for further information or to arrange an inspection.
